item.title: [+2961] School that banned Obama speech will bus kids to Bush speech
item.description: The Arlington Independent School District in Texas decided not to show President Obama’s address to students live yesterday because it reportedly didn’t want to interrupt its regularly scheduled lesson plans. However, the district has now decided to bus its students off-campus on Sept. 21 to hear President Bush speak. Texas FTL.
